the Bobomobile got abath
Posted on May 1, 2016 | Leave a comment
This car was donated by Marcia Bobo. It came with a minimum price. I was asked to pay when I could. I was also asked to pay the money as a donation to the Alzheimers Association. Pretty cool huh?
The Bobomobile has been from here to California and back two times with me. It uses a little oil, but not much.
